@startuml
title Course Addition – Component Overview

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Course Author" as Author

package "Minimal Course Files" as Files {
    [course.json\n//Title + Hole Info//\n(Course Info optional)] as JSON
    [course.tscn\n//3D Scene//] as TSCN
}

package "Course Selector" as Selector {
    [CourseValidator\ncourse_validator.gd] as CV
    [CourseList\ncourse_list.gd] as CL
    [CourseSelector\ncourse_selector.gd] as CS
}

[SceneManager\nscene_manager.gd] as SM

[CourseManager\ncourse_manager] as CM

note bottom of CM
  Defaults applied when
  Course Info is missing:
  • Tee Colors
  • Texture Indices
end note

Author --> JSON : create
Author --> TSCN : create

CV --> JSON : validate config & read title
CV --> TSCN : check scene exists
CL --> CV : validate each course dir

CS --> CL : discover courses\nget_scene_path\nget_config_path
CS --> SM : load_course(path, config_path)
SM --> CM : load CourseManager scene
CM --> JSON : parse & apply defaults
CM --> TSCN : load as child

@enduml
